<p>I try to compile all my css from my bower_components using bower_concat <a href="https://github.com/sapegin/grunt-bower-concat" rel="nofollow">https://github.com/sapegin/grunt-bower-concat</a>. The js compiles fine but the css never gets created. Here is my grunt file code for this section:</p>  <pre><code>  bower_concat: {             all: {                 dest: '&lt;%= pkg.dist_dir %&gt;/lib/_bower.js',                 cssDest: '&lt;%= pkg.dist_dir %&gt;/lib/_bower.css',                 dependencies: {                     // 'angular': ''                 },                 exclude: [                     'jquery'                 ],                 bowerOptions: {                     relative: false                 },                 includeDev: true             }         }, </code></pre>  <p>It never creates "_bower.css". Why is not working as it should?</p>